        <updateDate>2022-06-22T18:49:05Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Informing Veterans on Education for Transitioning Servicemembers Act of 2022 or the Informing VETS Act</strong> <strong>of 2022</strong><strong></strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to regularly promote the Veteran Readiness and Employment program by (1) sending a letter to each veteran entitled to the program that explains the educational benefits of the program, and (2) providing in each letter and online a side-by-side comparison of benefits between the program and Post-9/11 GI Bill educational assistance.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
